div.p:
WE have this Reading of the holy Scriptures in Order, recommended to us by the Aſſembly of Divines at Weſtminſter, in their Directory for Publick Worſhip, in theſe words;
It is requiſite that all the Canonical books, be read over in Order, that

the People may be better acquainted with the whole body of Scriptures.
